@Node HIST "The History of this Door..."

  -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
                          History of this Door
  -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

    Version 1.3 (23rd April 1997)
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Patched the Main Door Executable with Niki Murkett's Multitasking
       AMOS Patch which allows the program to be ran more than one copy
       at a time, which is intended for multi-node BBS's.
   
    Version 1.2 (19th March 1997)
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Corrected Some Major Bugs such as the one which didn't let the
       User Upload any Files [:)

   O - Added the Configuration File where the Sysop can set in which
       File Section the Raw Uploads go to and also set an Optional
       File Path (like MagicFile)

    Version 1.1 (10th February 1997) - Internal Version
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Heavily Bugged. Upload System did not even work at all

   O - Added `Upload More Files' Option

    Version 1.0 (1st February 1997) - Internal Version
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - This was not a Door, a Random Number Generator could have written
       better code than me on this version, So I re-wrote the entire
       Door. :p

   @{" [0] " Link MAIN} Return to the Main Menu

@EndNode HIST

